  "detailed_description": "Blade and Ham is a classic 2.5D beat'em up set in a fantasy world. <br><br><i>After ages of epic battles, blood and violence, wars and wonders... Heroes built a cozy tavern, for quiet life in ale and beer. But once, some one killed their dog...</i><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Characters</li></ul>6 unique heroes with different stats, movements and special attacks.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Knurs</li></ul>A magic creatures who helps you with healing, magic and even force.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Global Map</li></ul>Explore the world and track down the bastard!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752400/extras/2b967a6525c8a23304a89d44722e5e76.avif?t=1636997016\" width=620 height=410 /></span><br>* On the keyboard use WASD for movement and numpad for actions.",
